de.ovgu.featureide.cloneanalysis.impl

Class CloneOccurence

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.cloneanalysis.impl.CloneOccurence

  • public class CloneOccurence
extends java.lang.Object
    Data container object that holds the data of an occurence of a code clone, namely the file in which it was found and the line index at which the clone begins.
    Author:
    Konstantin Tonscheidt
    See Also:
    Clone, CloneAnalysisResults
